View sông cực đỉnh, cực hiếm, cực chất, đảm bảo làm hài lòng cả những vị khách khó tính nhất. Đừng chần chừ, cơ hội vàng này sẽ không chờ đợi ai! Liên hệ ĐÔNG NHÀ TO để được tư vấn và xem nhà ngay (Mr. Đông am hiểu sâu thị trường Long Biên & Gia Lâm): 0385206294 (Zalo). Rare Opportunity! A unique opportunity awaits discerning clients seeking a luxurious resort-style living space in Hanoi! The owner urgently needs to sell this stunning riverside villa, now offered with a deep discount of 3 billion VND. With an area of 360m2, this exquisitely designed villa comes fully furnished with high-end interiors, providing a 5-star resort living experience. Located in Long Bien, Hanoi, the villa boasts an outstanding, incredibly rare million-dollar river view, guaranteed to impress even the most discerning buyers at first sight. This is not only an ideal home for settling down and enjoying a year-round resort lifestyle, but also a profitable investment opportunity with the potential for renting to foreigners, generating excellent cash flow. Price just over 20 billion VND after the deep reduction. For interested buyers, please contact directly: 0385206294 (ĐÔNG NHÀ TO) for more details and to arrange a viewing.
